            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>onumentum</ex></expan> Sanuacae Cacusi <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>filia</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> viva sibi pos<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>it</abbr></expan> <lb n="3"/>et Sacirone <note>sic</note> mari<lb break="no" n="4"/>to Ulatti filio <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uo</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Handschriftlich überliefert. E mit zwei senkrechten Hasten wiedergegeben (sog. &amp;apos;gallisches&amp;apos; E).</p>
